<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA16">
<l>vantutaitta veṇṭiraikaḷ cempavaḷa veṇmutta</l>
<l>manti viḷakku maṇiviḷakkā – mentai</l>
<l>yoruvallit tāmaraiyā ḷoṉṟiyacīr mārpaṉ</l>
<l>ṟiruvallik kēṇiyāṉ ceṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The red corals [and] the white pearls from the white waves</l>
<l>that come [and] crash become decorative lamps that illuminate the dusk,</l>
<l>going to him of Tiruvallikēṇi, our father, the one with an excellent chest</l>
<l>that is one with her of the lotus, the unique creeper.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
